  "description": "<p>A compulsion is an almost irresistible urge to behave in a certain way that is usually detrimental or life-altering to the person with the compulsion. When your character gains a compulsion from being corrupted, they obsess over this behavior as either a coping mechanism for the stress they have been through or as a dark urge acted out as the corruption within them grows.</p>",
